== 电子护照 ==
土耳其符合[[国际民用航空组织|国际民用航空组织]]的新'''电子护照'''自2010年6月1日开始发行。申请人可通过政府网站提交申请，护照会通过邮寄方式送达。<ref>{{tr icon}} http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/ekonomi/14030770.asp?gid=373 {{Wayback|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/ekonomi/14030770.asp?gid=373 |date=20150924051036 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.epasaport.gov.tr/|title=e-Pasaport|publisher=|access-date=2016-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130704025837/http://www.epasaport.gov.tr/|archive-date=2013-07-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/14368911.asp|title=Atalay: Çipli pasaport başvurusu online olacak|author=Mehmet Kayhan YILDIZ- Taner ORAL- İhsan YALÇIN/KONYA, (DHA)|date=2010-04-09|publisher=|accessdate=2016-04-03|archive-date=2012-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017032121/http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/14368911.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{tr icon}} http://www.hurriyet.de/haberler/gundem/363040/cagdas-pasaport-yolda {{Wayback|url=http://www.hurriyet.de/haberler/gundem/363040/cagdas-pasaport-yolda |date=20110728130905 }}</ref>

